# API 엔드포인트 가이드

## 마이그레이션 API

### 공개 엔드포인트 (비활성화)
- `/api/migration/*` → 항상 503 (`lib/migration/http-migration-guard.ts`)
- 예전 `status` / `start` / `artists` 경로는 존재하지 않음

### Secure 마이그레이션 (인증 필요)
- [app/api/secure/migration/check-status/route.ts](mdc:app/api/secure/migration/check-status/route.ts): GET, admin
- [app/api/secure/migration/detect-tables/route.ts](mdc:app/api/secure/migration/detect-tables/route.ts): GET, system
- [app/api/secure/migration/migrate-all/route.ts](mdc:app/api/secure/migration/migrate-all/route.ts): POST, system

## 동기화 API

### Secure 동기화 제어
- [app/api/secure/sync/start/route.ts](mdc:app/api/secure/sync/start/route.ts)
- [app/api/secure/sync/stop/route.ts](mdc:app/api/secure/sync/stop/route.ts)
- [app/api/secure/sync/status/route.ts](mdc:app/api/secure/sync/status/route.ts)

## 데이터 API

### Artists 관리
- [app/api/artists/route.ts](mdc:app/api/artists/route.ts): Artists CRUD
- [app/api/artists/[id]/route.ts](mdc:app/api/artists/[id]/route.ts): 개별 Artist

### Artworks 관리
- [app/api/artworks/route.ts](mdc:app/api/artworks/route.ts): Artworks CRUD

## API 사용법
```javascript
// 마이그레이션 상태 확인 (관리자 세션 필요)
const response = await fetch('/api/secure/migration/check-status')
const status = await response.json()

// 마이그레이션 실행 (system/admin 권한 필요)
await fetch('/api/secure/migration/migrate-all', { method: 'POST' })
```

## 인증 및 보안
- 공개 `/api/migration/*`는 비활성화
- Secure API는 `createAdminAPI` / `createSystemAPI` + rate limit + audit log
- CSRF는 middleware Origin/Referer guard로 처리
